        <mxCell id="legend-flow" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=left;fontSize=9;fontColor=#cccccc;" value="&lt;div style=&#39;text-align:left;line-height:1.8;&#39;&gt;1. User → &lt;b style=&#39;color:#e94560&#39;&gt;nara CLI&lt;/b&gt; → &lt;b&gt;Orchestrator&lt;/b&gt; routes intent&lt;br&gt;2. &lt;b style=&#39;color:#00d2ff&#39;&gt;Scanner&lt;/b&gt; runs Semgrep + Bandit on host → structured findings&lt;br&gt;3. &lt;b style=&#39;color:#f5a623&#39;&gt;Planner&lt;/b&gt; designs kill chain from findings → ordered steps&lt;br&gt;4. &lt;b style=&#39;color:#e94560&#39;&gt;Exploiter&lt;/b&gt; provisions container → fires exploits via &lt;code&gt;docker exec&lt;/code&gt; → deploys ransomware&lt;br&gt;5. Desktop effects visible via &lt;b style=&#39;color:#e94560&#39;&gt;noVNC&lt;/b&gt; at &lt;code&gt;localhost:6080&lt;/code&gt; in browser&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="80" width="650" x="75" y="755" as="geometry" />
